Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你真是一點都沒有變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  和小時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,個子長高了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且比那時候更強了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…這個人是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（奈多流與那塔魯同音，神明與真名同音，至於全名就是「真名那塔魯」）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  神明奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在用這個名字更加合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  和我「有田紫苑」的名字一個道理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑嗎  很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那塔魯你是什麼時候來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…  那時候還未與巴迪說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經差不多過了14年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裡以後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣很渾濁  人口也過剩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到處戰火不斷的半文明星球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阿留多人不會遭到歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你也記得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中心塔恐怖襲擊後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(296,362)}Central Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對待阿留多人的歧視和迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在被隔離營收容之前  我和老爸勉勉強強得以逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  最後到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉  淨說些陰鬱的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來  巴迪現在在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我當了聯邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  有什麼事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  搜查當中的秘密是不能說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  長大了呢  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個尿床後就哭的巴迪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這種事情你居然還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的人是青梅竹馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我和早宮一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪也欺負過那塔魯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  中心塔恐怖襲擊是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的虎球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(396,362)}tradama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是精神創傷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(370,362)}trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕  學校學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我逮捕到迪安謝路之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經被某人殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很難想像地球人能夠殺得了蓋澤人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是內訌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼逮捕剩餘逃犯就更為重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握到了一些線索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是擬態反應芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如使用者的生命反應消失的場合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它就會消除屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是已經預載了消滅證據的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是最新的古拉那達型芯片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是會在這種邊境星球出售的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也會試著調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎  不報告那塔魯的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦  他又不是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  在地球的阿留多人難民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼稀罕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓他平靜地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「是誰說有宇宙人來了的」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  是誰說出這種像REAL廚一般的話來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（REAl廚房：廚房是對網路上發出幼稚言論的人的蔑稱，簡稱廚。\NREAl廚並非指全年齡的廚，而是對真正的中學生，而且是廚的人的稱呼。\N現在用法上多數含有嘲諷自己的中學時代的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(100,290)\fs22}神 室戶的書中寫到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 是我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是宇宙人的目擊帖祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  有好多UFO圖片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千明你相信UFO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是太相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在誰還會相信存在著宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個看來很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公開被懷疑與「高級賓館，迷之失蹤事件」有關的女性肖像畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比幼稚園小鬼的塗鴉還臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算是一種天才吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男生真是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  別把我和他們歸為一類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小卡貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖…咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你！全是因為你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是擬態反應芯片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼的話就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…  下個月有田紫苑的日程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是預定得滿滿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  會做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的「阿留多人網路」是有很長歷史的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是聯絡各個亡命流浪到此地的人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是傳言最近從聯邦出來的人裡出現了「亡命專家」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亡命專家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的話  走私擬態反應芯片也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡？  那「亡命專家」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也調查一下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  島野醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態如何？ 還在吃藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼需要的話  隨時都可以和我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  在那裡的是你女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是怎麼來到地球的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  想問問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查中的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我還只是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是按照老爸說的逃跑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  能問下你爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  出了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很久沒有聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在是否還活著也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子知道她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼奈多流會和笨蛋偶像在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青梅竹馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈多流   還記得明天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴…有田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以後再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了什麼讓那孩子不高興的事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說翔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看她好像生氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為巴迪和那塔魯看起來關係很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子的少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少女心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子喜歡那塔魯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入戀情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  說得像是都明白了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你沒戀愛過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒空去發情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才懶得管地球人的發情衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啦  洗澡去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  今天是你哥哥的月忌日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我抽時間去看一下他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也只能做這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是受到你的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你們家對我有還不清的恩情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼恩情  都是一千年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過才一千年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  那個人又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個人  要叫依露瑪女士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  依露瑪女士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸  盆栽可是老爺爺的興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你總有一天會知道其好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是並不怎麼想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我不在的時候來過這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪安謝路的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  真危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別用那力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那份力量會毀了你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸果然也上了年紀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西  我不會用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那老太婆真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道當初是哪裡的哪個傢伙在這裡哭著央求的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能活下去全都虧了依露瑪女士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi  小卡貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是特製的咖啡  巴迪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在特務中曾被譽為「死神」的我竟然淪落到這份…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全怪那個笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了一個有趣的傳聞哦  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？ 不愧是依露瑪  告訴我告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  要是你繼續「有田紫苑的工作」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  布偶裝的主持就拜託了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有個帶有卡魯貝蘭托人味道的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡？  在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是在青山的後街附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}（青山：東京都港區內的高級住宅區）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡貝拉  來收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真浪費呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喝掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你還有誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是卡魯貝蘭托人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  拜託收集卡魯貝蘭托人的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉茲涅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罪犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標接近？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪  很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被誰看到了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是阿格拉茲涅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以越獄嫌疑逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是認錯人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  車終於送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是二手的  但還是嶄新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  我的嶄新嶄新二手車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  請上車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他想逃進六本木廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒有護罩還是有點吃力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡帝托的探索也無法發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  這個星球有搜查官在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉茲涅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧  殺了迪安謝路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是罪有應得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是阿留多人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑阿留多人能把我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和迪安謝路可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我用這手把你撚死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  那可真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會給你個痛快的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？  被阿留多人扯斷胳膊的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這星球的人很像阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以覺得在這裡試驗硫加也沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原住民全都死了也沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正死的也是像阿留多人一樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別急嘛  各務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電影都開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看下一場不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼好著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  翔子發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各務  剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各務？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各務 ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我…  求你放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飽嘗過痛苦  去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩5人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:14.50,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi 我是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉的說～
